    "name": "Keil and Delitzsch Biblical Commentary on the Old Testament",
    "elements": [
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "Then one of the sons of Elam, Shecaniah, the son of Jehiel, stood forth from amidst the assembly, and uttered the confession: \"We have been unfaithful towards our God by marrying strange wives, but there is yet hope for Israel concerning this thing. We will now make a covenant with God to put away all the strange wives and their children from the congregation, according to the counsel of the Lord, and of those who fear the commandment of our God, that it may be done according to the law.\" Shecaniah, of the sons of Elam (comp. ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 2:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 8:7",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "), is a different person from the descendant of Zattu, mentioned ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 8:5",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": "; nor is Jehiel identical with the individual whose name occurs in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 10:26",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "",
        "text": ". ונּשׁב, and have brought home strange wives. הושׁיב, to cause to dwell (in one's house), said in ",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
        "class": "verse-link",
        "text": "Ezra 10:10",
        "children": []
      },
      {
        "element": "span",
